HEADWORD: Buprestidan
<hw>Bu*pres"ti*dan</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>buprestis</ets>, Gr. <?/, a poisonous beetle, which, being eaten by
